algref

Class BookPublication

  • java.lang.Object
    • algref.Publication
      • algref.BookPublication

  • public class BookPublication
extends Publication
    Objects of this class represent book publications. The representational fields already exist in the parent class, but this indicates the appropriate type to the bibtex conversion component, as well as ignoring the start and end page numbers, as they are unnecessary.
